{"tid":863193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<Fake news都咁> CNN民調出爐！川普2020拚連任可望獲勝","createTime":"2018-10-15T11:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T15:17:20.000Z","uid":62257,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbbc170da40df9a521c565a874d8421e28f1196","tid":863193,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連fake news 民調都有46%?!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2580900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2580900&d=mXFPMEQdJt9qzdVrfsY5B2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=87e0a7a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2580900&h=34f33d53\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2580900</a><br />\n2018-10-15 09:25<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕川普聲勢旺？根據美媒《CNN》委託市調機構「SSRS」的結果顯示，越來越多美國人認為，川普可能在2020年競選連任時獲勝，至於美國前副總統拜登（Joe Biden），則被認為最可能代表民主黨角逐下屆美國總統大選。<br />\n<br />\n民調結果顯示，美國人對川普的看好度越來越高，有46%民眾認為川普競選連任可能當選，另外有47%認為不會當選。數據指出，自從3月以來，川普的看好度不斷攀升，其中男性增加8個百分點，看好川普的中間選民也從3月的39%增至47%。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨支持者方面，有74％的共和黨人和偏向共和黨的中間選民認為，川普應該在2020年被共和黨提名，僅21％的人持相反意見。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨方面，拜登以33％的支持位居榜首，佛蒙特州的參議員桑德斯（Bernie Sanders）以13％則排第二，其次為加州參議員卡馬拉哈里斯（Kamala Harris）的9%看好度。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日前才註冊成為民主黨人的紐約前市長彭博（Michael Bloomberg）則拿下4%看好度。"},{"pid":"291d396fb997d4323c93a5fb65fbc26c0ef86466","tid":863193,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfe53ffda03479dc5ee7358623704e818c4e618","tid":863193,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7ac1fbced9811a315c99dbe4fde3bb12fdf2a6","tid":863193,"uid":1886,"like":